Package: whichdist
Type: Package
Title: Assess the Best-Fitting Distribution For a Count Variable
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Amanda Wang
Maintainer: Amanda Wang <amanda.m.wang21@gmail.com>
Description: With this function, the user can input a continuous count metric they aim to use as the outcome variable in an analysis and assess which type of regression to run.    
     Potential suggestions include OLS linear regression, poisson regression, negative binomial regression, zero-inflated poisson regression, and zero-inflated negative binomial regression.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
